            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EHarvest%20is%20a%20time%20of%20high%20motivation%2C%20a%20time%20when%20all%20the%20efforts%20of%20an%20entire%20year%20come%20to%20fruition.%20How%20can%20someone%20sleep%20if%20the%20grain%20is%20standing%20ready%20and%20a%20storm%20is%20coming%20that%20can%20ruin%20it%3F%20If%20people%20sleep%2C%20they%20are%20wasting%20the%20blood%2C%20sweat%2C%20and%20tears%20of%20all%20the%20laborers%20before%20them.%20They%20are%20turning%20their%20backs%20on%20the%20financial%20rewards%20the%20harvest%20will%20bring%20at%20the%20market.%20They%20are%20wasting%20their%20day%20of%20opportunity.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJesus%20spoke%20of%20those%20who%20receive%20the%20Word%20but%20are%20distracted%20by%20lives%20of%20ease%20and%20pleasure.%20Although%20the%20harvest%20is%20ripe%2C%20they%20are%20busy%20pursuing%20the%20things%20of%20this%20world.%20He%20reminded%20us%20that%20others%2C%20however%2C%20would%20be%20wise%20sons%20or%20daughters%20who%20would%20gather%20thirtyfold%2C%20sixtyfold%2C%20and%20a%20hundredfold%20in%20the%20day%20of%20harvest%20(Mark%204%3A20).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20are%20now%20in%20the%20period%20of%20the%20greatest%20spiritual%20harvest%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20seen.%20Hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20new%20Christians%20are%20being%20saved%20every%20day.%20Lay%20aside%20your%20sleep%20and%20wake%20up!%20Your%20summer%20of%20harvest%20may%20never%20happen%20again%20this%20side%20of%20eternity.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
