            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Leviticus.7:28-9:6",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ELeviticus%207%3A28-9%3A6%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_28%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Portion%20for%20the%20Priests%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Moses%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_29%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGive%20the%20following%20instructions%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20When%20you%20present%20a%20peace%20offering%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20bring%20part%20of%20it%20as%20a%20gift%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_30%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EPresent%20it%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20with%20your%20own%20hands%20as%20a%20special%20gift%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Bring%20the%20fat%20of%20the%20animal%2C%20together%20with%20the%20breast%2C%20and%20lift%20up%20the%20breast%20as%20a%20special%20offering%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_31%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20priest%20will%20burn%20the%20fat%20on%20the%20altar%2C%20but%20the%20breast%20will%20belong%20to%20Aaron%20and%20his%20descendants.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_32%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EGive%20the%20right%20thigh%20of%20your%20peace%20offering%20to%20the%20priest%20as%20a%20gift.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_33%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20right%20thigh%20must%20always%20be%20given%20to%20the%20priest%20who%20offers%20the%20blood%20and%20the%20fat%20of%20the%20peace%20offering.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_34%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20I%20have%20reserved%20the%20breast%20of%20the%20special%20offering%20and%20the%20right%20thigh%20of%20the%20sacred%20offering%20for%20the%20priests.%20It%20is%20the%20permanent%20right%20of%20Aaron%20and%20his%20descendants%20to%20share%20in%20the%20peace%20offerings%20brought%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_35%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20their%20rightful%20share.%20The%20special%20gifts%20presented%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20have%20been%20reserved%20for%20Aaron%20and%20his%20descendants%20from%20the%20time%20they%20were%20set%20apart%20to%20serve%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20as%20priests.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_36%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20the%20day%20they%20were%20anointed%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20commanded%20the%20Israelites%20to%20give%20these%20portions%20to%20the%20priests%20as%20their%20permanent%20share%20from%20generation%20to%20generation.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_37%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20instructions%20for%20the%20burnt%20offering%2C%20the%20grain%20offering%2C%20the%20sin%20offering%2C%20and%20the%20guilt%20offering%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20ordination%20offering%20and%20the%20peace%20offering.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_7_38%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2238%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E38%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20these%20instructions%20to%20Moses%20on%20Mount%20Sinai%20when%20he%20commanded%20the%20Israelites%20to%20present%20their%20offerings%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20the%20wilderness%20of%20Sinai.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_1%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ELeviticus%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EOrdination%20of%20the%20Priests%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Moses%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_2%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBring%20Aaron%20and%20his%20sons%2C%20along%20with%20their%20sacred%20garments%2C%20the%20anointing%20oil%2C%20the%20bull%20for%20the%20sin%20offering%2C%20the%20two%20rams%2C%20and%20the%20basket%20of%20bread%20made%20without%20yeast%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_3%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20call%20the%20entire%20community%20of%20Israel%20together%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Tabernacle.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ETent%20of%20Meeting%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%208%3A4%2C%2031%2C%2033%2C%2035.%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_4%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Moses%20followed%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20instructions%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20community%20assembled%20at%20the%20Tabernacle%20entrance.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_5%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EMoses%20announced%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20commanded%20us%20to%20do!%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_6%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20presented%20Aaron%20and%20his%20sons%20and%20washed%20them%20with%20water.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_7%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20put%20the%20official%20tunic%20on%20Aaron%20and%20tied%20the%20sash%20around%20his%20waist.%20He%20dressed%20him%20in%20the%20robe%2C%20placed%20the%20ephod%20on%20him%2C%20and%20attached%20the%20ephod%20securely%20with%20its%20decorative%20sash.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_8%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20placed%20the%20chestpiece%20on%20Aaron%20and%20put%20the%20Urim%20and%20the%20Thummim%20inside%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_9%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20placed%20the%20turban%20on%20Aaron%26%23x2019%3Bs%20head%20and%20attached%20the%20gold%20medallion%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20badge%20of%20holiness%26%23x2014%3Bto%20the%20front%20of%20the%20turban%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20commanded%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_10%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20took%20the%20anointing%20oil%20and%20anointed%20the%20Tabernacle%20and%20everything%20in%20it%2C%20making%20them%20holy.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_11%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20sprinkled%20the%20oil%20on%20the%20altar%20seven%20times%2C%20anointing%20it%20and%20all%20its%20utensils%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20washbasin%20and%20its%20stand%2C%20making%20them%20holy.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_12%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20poured%20some%20of%20the%20anointing%20oil%20on%20Aaron%26%23x2019%3Bs%20head%2C%20anointing%20him%20and%20making%20him%20holy%20for%20his%20work.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_13%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3ENext%20Moses%20presented%20Aaron%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sons.%20He%20clothed%20them%20in%20their%20tunics%2C%20tied%20their%20sashes%20around%20them%2C%20and%20put%20their%20special%20head%20coverings%20on%20them%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20commanded%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_14%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20presented%20the%20bull%20for%20the%20sin%20offering.%20Aaron%20and%20his%20sons%20laid%20their%20hands%20on%20the%20bull%26%23x2019%3Bs%20head%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_15%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20Moses%20slaughtered%20it.%20Moses%20took%20some%20of%20the%20blood%2C%20and%20with%20his%20finger%20he%20put%20it%20on%20the%20four%20horns%20of%20the%20altar%20to%20purify%20it.%20He%20poured%20out%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20blood%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20altar.%20Through%20this%20process%2C%20he%20made%20the%20altar%20holy%20by%20purifying%20it.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A15%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eby%20making%20atonement%20for%20it%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Ethat%20offerings%20for%20purification%20might%20be%20made%20on%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_16%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20took%20all%20the%20fat%20around%20the%20internal%20organs%2C%20the%20long%20lobe%20of%20the%20liver%2C%20and%20the%20two%20kidneys%20and%20the%20fat%20around%20them%2C%20and%20he%20burned%20it%20all%20on%20the%20altar.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_17%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20took%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20bull%2C%20including%20its%20hide%2C%20meat%2C%20and%20dung%2C%20and%20burned%20it%20on%20a%20fire%20outside%20the%20camp%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20commanded%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_8_18%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20presented%20the%20ram%20for%20the%20burnt%20offering.%20